Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.63,0:01:04.51,Ginny,,0,0,0,,I'm not Harry Potter's girlfriend anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:07.98,Ginny,,0,0,0,,I might as well be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:10.40,Moaning Myrtle,,0,0,0,,Well, don't do it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:14.74,Moaning Myrtle,,0,0,0,,The last thing this castle needs is a whiny bitch,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:19.89,Moaning Myrtle,,0,0,0,,stalking the hallways and the bathrooms. And your voice is annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:29.14,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:34.08,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Diary time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:38.97,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Okay... Dear diary,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.77,0:01:40.97,Ginny,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:42.97,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Ginny uuuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.97,0:01:45.55,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Today my whole world fell apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:48.35,Ginny,,0,0,0,,My boyfriend dumped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:50.53,Ginny,,0,0,0,,And you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:53.42,Ginny,,0,0,0,,I'm done with him!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:55.42,Ginny,,0,0,0,,*harrumph*
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:57.55,Ginny,,0,0,0,,I hate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:59.24,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me, diary???
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:02.53,Ginny,,0,0,0,,I HATE HARRY POTTER!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Laughter out of thin air]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:08.19,Tom,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:12.66,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Huuuuuh???
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:15.57,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Huuuuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:17.92,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:21.48,Tom,,0,0,0,,Somebody who understands you, Ginny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:26.48,Tom,,0,0,0,,Somebody who knows what it's like to be filled... with hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.92,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Diary...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:33.12,Tom,,0,0,0,,I'm a journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:37.29,Tom,,0,0,0,,Not a diary, diaries are for girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.31,Tom,,0,0,0,,But yes, Ginny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:44.14,Tom,,0,0,0,,I'm a magic diary - Shit! Journal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:48.03,Tom,,0,0,0,,I'm a magic journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:51.79,Tom,,0,0,0,,Enchanted with the spirit of it's former owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.26,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.12,Tom,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.29,Ginny,,0,0,0,,But Harry gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:59.85,Tom,,0,0,0,,*sigh* read the name on the cover, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.85,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Oh. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.21,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:10.67,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Mar...Mar...Marvel... Mar... Mar...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:13.14,Tom,,0,0,0,,Okay, just... *sigh* just skip that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:16.41,Tom,,0,0,0,,It's a made up name for this letter re-arranging trick. You'll... you'll find out later, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.72,Tom,,0,0,0,,Go to... Go to the next name!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:21.14,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ridle! [No mistake ;-)]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.91,Tom,,0,0,0,,...Yeah. Tom Riddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.25,Tom,,0,0,0,,I'm a piece of his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:34.22,Tom,,0,0,0,,Separated from the whole and bound to this diary. Shit! Journal!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:37.39,Tom,,0,0,0,,Bound to this f****** JOUR-NAL!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.66,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Oh, but what do you want, diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:44.43,Tom,,0,0,0,,To help you, Ginny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:47.09,Tom,,0,0,0,,That's what journals are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:50.67,Tom,,0,0,0,,See: I once was like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.84,Tom,,0,0,0,,Alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.59,Tom,,0,0,0,,angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:57.78,Tom,,0,0,0,,The world had... turned it's back on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.82,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Oh, what did you do, diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:02.82,Tom,,0,0,0,,Let me show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.32,Tom,,0,0,0,,In a magic flashback...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.29,Tom,,0,0,0,,It all started, when I was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:11.88,Tom,,0,0,0,,An orphan boy \N[Reference to: A Very Potter Musical]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lights down on Ginny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lights up on the magic flashback.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We find ourselves at Wool's orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:28.94,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,I think you'll find Wool's orphanage is a first rate establishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.84,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,We have seven different breeds of orphan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.14,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,including street urchin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:36.14,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,rosy cheeked,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:38.14,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,delightfully small,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:42.53,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,and one little evil telekinetic Antichrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:46.02,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,Now, what was it you're interested in today, Mr. ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:48.82,Dumbledore,,0,0,0,,Dumbledore! Albus Dumbledore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.44,Dumbledore,,0,0,0,,But you could call me Dumby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.74,Dumbledore,,0,0,0,,Or ah... Big D. \N[Reference to: A Very Potter Sequel]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:05:00.14,Dumbledore,,0,0,0,,You know, ah... The D stands for, aaah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.72,Dumbledore,,0,0,0,,...my doctorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:06.11,Dumbledore,,0,0,0,,I'm a Professor at a school for very magical children, ah f***ing shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.62,Dumbledore,,0,0,0,,I mean: Very regular children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:09.39,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:17.36,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,Well, you're in luck, big D, because we've plenty of those in stock, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:22.21,Dumbledore,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well just listen doll-face: I'm here to see one little cutie in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:24.49,Dumbledore,,0,0,0,,That ah... Tom Riddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.17,Dumbledore,,0,0,0,,I think he might be just right for our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:31.02,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,Oh... Tom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.52,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,, ...Riddle... ?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:35.65,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:40.06,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,But I warn you: This boy's a monster!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.53,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,Tho- Thomas...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:50.74,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,You ha... you... you have a visitor, Professor Dumbledore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.45,Dumbledore,,0,0,0,,How do you do, Tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:54.92,Tom,,0,0,0,,Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:57.55,Tom,,0,0,0,,Like a Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:01.40,Tom,,0,0,0,,So they've come here to take... a look at me, have they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:03.98,Tom,,0,0,0,,Well, there's nothing wrong with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:07.45,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,Just stop shouting, Mr. man! He is from a school!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:11.87,Mrs. Cole,,0,0,0,,He might just take you off my hands, you filthy little heathen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:16.93,Dumbledore,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Mrs. Cole! I think I can take it from here, now get the hell out of here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.62,Tom,,0,0,0,,Why don't you get out of here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.62,Tom,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna want me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:26.85,Tom,,0,0,0,,She's right, you know?
